{"tid":1875284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［聯署要人］阻止黑警使用電槍！","createTime":"2020-02-11T16:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T12:02:23.000Z","uid":8435,"like":77,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"092935b49b1a725ee4124497e3145453ac3edc11","tid":1875284,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:32:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">仲有3日就到期<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲爭48305個簽名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-konger-strongly-hope-usa-can-warning-hong-kong-police-cant-adding-electric-gun-new-weapon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-konger-strongly-hope-usa-can-warning-hong-kong-police-cant-adding-electric-gun-new-weapon&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BVNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=c7bc1fdb\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-konger-strongly-hope-usa-can-warning-hong-kong-police-cant-adding-electric-gun-new-weapon</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人民希望美國聯邦政府為電鎗向香港警察作出實質性的警告及發出禁止通知書。<br />\n<br />\n在2020年1月15日，香港警務處處長正在考慮增加電鎗作為新的警察裝備。電鎗比催淚氣體和胡椒噴霧更致命。<br />\n<br />\n==============================<br />\n有巴打好有心做咗個聯署bot<br />\n可以bookmark咗佢隔幾日上去睇下有咩聯署未簽<br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BVNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=f631e29d\" target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a>"},{"pid":"5424a5c2eb0d858e6e73c5d2b531402ae94a3255","tid":1875284,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:32:44.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"6a21a04e60692fe202cf4ce968ea0adbc4f9f920","tid":1875284,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:32:57.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"e3247a7ee036